Package: BatChef
Title: Single-cell batch effects correction methods
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
     c(person("Elena", "Zuin", , "elena.zuin.3@phd.unipd.it", role = c("aut", "cre")),
     person("Davide", "Risso", , "davide.risso@unipd.it", role = "ctb"),
     person("Gabriele", "Sales", , "gabriele.sales@unipd.it", role = "ctb"))
Description: Contains a common interface for single-cell batch correction methods in R and Python environments. 
  This includes methods based on different strategies, such as mutually nearest neighbors, graph-based, and deep learning. 
  Also, it provides some metrics to evaluate the performance.
